@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zxptys(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs((v0 * (v2 + 0.25 - v1 + 0.88)))
    v2 = 0.04
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.10 * tmp + 0.46)) - ((v0 + 0.56 + v0 + 0.32) * 0.62))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.60 - v2 + 0.80)) + wp.abs(v1))
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.46 / v1 + 0.50) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.57)) * tmp)
    v2 = v2
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
